quote.p:
Georgiana, British, 407 tons register; brig rig; cargo, merchandise,
                            provisions, and drugs; no guns on deck; no fitting for guns on board;
                            one cwt. powder; iron bulwarks; no port-holes for guns; no fittings for
                            guns on board; a fast vessel; forty, crew; not fitted as a privateer;
                            better adapted for running the blockade; cleared out for Nassau; now in
                            the Mersey, and is intended to leave to-day, say 4 p.m.
